{"tid":667213,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"物理神人幫幫手2 (美國佬回覆！)","createTime":"2018-05-16T14:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T12:31:53.000Z","uid":9506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7a36c2e11db6bcdabb54731f349ddfd7fe9e725c","tid":667213,"uid":9506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:15:36.000Z","msg":"事關小弟上次開post得到各路英雄指點後，就咁樣覆個美國教授：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/221119_0af5ee7c8a3e4801aaad16727a4914ab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F221119_0af5ee7c8a3e4801aaad16727a4914ab.png&h=172beb42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住過咗幾日，個教授就咁樣覆番我：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/221136_4ab5422278870b389352830ad889c8bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F221136_4ab5422278870b389352830ad889c8bc.png&h=ec5b718e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇黎各位連登大神教得小弟實在太好，所以今次無畀佢屌柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw，宜家再問下大家，我應該點知去再完善／修改我段解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，事關佢好似想提出(1)spring-mass system係受住periodic driving force而出現唔同phase angle既vibration同埋(2)Hooke's law好似唔多岩用係呢個case(如果我話唔同mass既inertia/acceleration唔同又可唔可行)？<br />\n<br />\n希望各位物理大神再次高抬貴手，thanksss<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055d21ba8f234b7cde0a154eddb13b46bd354500","tid":667213,"uid":9506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:16:38.000Z","msg":"原post:<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/660935/page/3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/660935/page/3</a>"},{"pid":"a7f98565942751b340678cf76097036b2d3028a4","tid":667213,"uid":9506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T15:00:48.000Z","msg":"pushhhhhh"},{"pid":"3e422464e94410bf81e8992bb17bbefcf60ab04e","tid":667213,"uid":171256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T17:22:07.000Z","msg":"你介唔介意quote埋，你send比教授嘅email<br />\n<br />\n我唔肯定係唔係prof get錯野<br />\n<br />\n佢話Hooke&rsquo;s law未必適用，可能係指<br />\n1) spring唔係massless(佢get錯？定係佢比為你想問realistic case)<br />\n2) extension &gt; proportionality limit<br />\n3) spring 可能會彎左<br />\n4) extension of spring requires time. 你periodic force嘅frequency如何？would the period of the force be less than the time for &ldquo;quasi-static&rdquo; equilibrium<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實，我覺得你應該pose多d assumptions<br />\ne.g. F= Fo cos(wt) ?<br />\n<br />\n再者，真係要solve咁多條ODE, 我地都係assume佢係SHM<br />\n<br />\n1) x_n = A_n exp(wt)<br />\n2) then solve homogenous equations <br />\n     find eigenvalue and then eigenvector<br />\n<br />\n我建議你睇左d example 先，我下面quote some examples"},{"pid":"152ea0dfcbec8fba19b118222eb655885d37bde7","tid":667213,"uid":171256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T17:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/17/013052_b27d65a5b6ebf7d8c4c46ee561311ab0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F17%2F013052_b27d65a5b6ebf7d8c4c46ee561311ab0.png&h=e483272e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/17/013057_1d916414c952191e4f9f550ca27e526c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F17%2F013057_1d916414c952191e4f9f550ca27e526c.png&h=38223e7a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/17/013101_2dd9a98a0c566bad91d5420e92ce2b42.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F17%2F013101_2dd9a98a0c566bad91d5420e92ce2b42.png&h=4604355e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/17/013105_c4c50a7358b6b15c183c0d2ca08e2424.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F17%2F013105_c4c50a7358b6b15c183c0d2ca08e2424.png&h=9cf67b0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4513de934ef23a3d95fe74206982bed8a97eea6","tid":667213,"uid":171256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T17:38:27.000Z","msg":"我諗呢個chapter應該係你想要嘅野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/17/013708_2d606644b3f46c88c28ee3007948cf91.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F17%2F013708_2d606644b3f46c88c28ee3007948cf91.png&h=7cd6d4bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/17/013710_546c4a363ca2db7582c474a48c40ed5d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F17%2F013710_546c4a363ca2db7582c474a48c40ed5d.png&h=e59ef741&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/17/013712_df2036355fe50d0796c659cc0abe4ede.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F17%2F013712_df2036355fe50d0796c659cc0abe4ede.png&h=7744fb5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba5e502232546c49caf261eeb6d7d183b71a9c3e","tid":667213,"uid":132660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T02:24:58.000Z","msg":"紅色字似係錯佐因果關係<br />\n個system唔係為佐(in order to) 要有non-trivial ossilation而phase angle唔同<br />\n啲mass有唔同displacement 與 佢地嘅phase angle唔同 係同一現象嘅不同解釋<br />\n原po巴打個point係一個好好嘅思路去了解個system做緊咩，但唔係<strong>點解</strong>個system會咁做<br />\nProf. quote紅字想講依點就係個system唔係為佐要拉長壓縮啲spring而有唔同phase angle<br />\n<br />\nphase angle好似同個initial condition有關...<br />\n<br />\n個人見解，lm學野，classical mechanics等炒..."},{"pid":"b1fd72f6ba414c90ada8fdd6ca2b7c0bf22f9625","tid":667213,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T03:36:10.000Z","msg":"我覺得係你寫個陣因果倒轉左<br />\n可能係因為英文文法問題<br />\n<br />\nThose masses has different phase angle is due to the difference of each weight and the property of each springs<br />\n<br />\n我會咁寫<br />\n但係我英文都唔係話好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等英文高手指教"},{"pid":"756475f7340709e5a53a134dee618961121acb3e","tid":667213,"uid":111749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a36c2e11db6bcdabb54731f349ddfd7fe9e725c","tid":667213,"uid":9506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:15:36.000Z","msg":"事關小弟上次開post得到各路英雄指點後，就咁樣覆個美國教授：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/221119_0af5ee7c8a3e4801aaad16727a4914ab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F221119_0af5ee7c8a3e4801aaad16727a4914ab.png&h=172beb42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住過咗幾日，個教授就咁樣覆番我：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/16/221136_4ab5422278870b389352830ad889c8bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2F221136_4ab5422278870b389352830ad889c8bc.png&h=ec5b718e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇黎各位連登大神教得小弟實在太好，所以今次無畀佢屌柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw，宜家再問下大家，我應該點知去再完善／修改我段解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，事關佢好似想提出(1)spring-mass system係受住periodic driving force而出現唔同phase angle既vibration同埋(2)Hooke's law好似唔多岩用係呢個case(如果我話唔同mass既inertia/acceleration唔同又可唔可行)？<br />\n<br />\n希望各位物理大神再次高抬貴手，thanksss<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:31:53.000Z","msg":"可能我之前講得唔好 就好似上面幾位巴打咁講 我個解法係調番轉個因果關係去容易啲visualise個system <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於佢話Hooke&rsquo;s law, 我諗佢唔想你go through啲ODE 不過我覺得老老實實go through一次上面巴打啲notes 拎住啲mathematical form黎睇就易明好多<br />\n<br />\n如果你教授係講緊external vibrator 同mass spring system之間有phase lag, 呢個真係要解一次條ode先容易明白<br />\n因為個phase lag depends on driving frequency 同 spring-mass既natural frequency (即係冇driving force既harmonic oscillation), 如果driving frequency遠細於natural frequency, 就好似平移緊個system咁, system個oscillation會同external oscillator in phase, 如果driving frequency遠大於natural frequency, 你可以用番inertia, 個system想stay at rest, 所以會anti phase, 如果係driving frequency = natural frequency, 就會係resonance, 呢個時候個system會岩岩好90度out of phase<br />\n<br />\n不過其實係俾咩人睇, 你教授唔想hand-waiving又唔想math-heavy真係有啲難搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}